### **🔹 Purpose of This Note**

The **Lion of Anacostia** is a structured **AI ethics and bias detection research framework** within the **Anacostia Vault**. This project integrates **machine learning, Africana studies, and algorithmic justice** to critically analyze bias in AI systems.

